original: Dahl, Jenny Gunhild Ingeborg, läroverksadjunkt, Skövde, f. 21/6/91 i Nybro av bankkas’sör J. P. DaM o. h. h. — Studiex. v. Gbgs h. latin 11, fil. kand. i Lund 13, fil. mag. 15, provår v. Sthlms folkskrsem. 17. Resor t. Norge 15 o. 35, Danm. 21, Tyskl., Ös-terr. o. Schweiz 22, Finl. 27, Tyskl. 31, Bsitl. 41. E. O’, foillksikoilili. 15, e.o. ämneis-Jär. i TomeliMa 15-16, Me-llerud 16, Ronneby o. Huskvarna 18-19, ord. äm-meslär. i Karlskoga 19, ämne.slär. v. Skövde h. a. 1. 29, adj. där ised. 39.
translated: Dahl, Jenny Gunhild Ingeborg, high school teacher, Skövde, born on June 21, 1891 in Nybro to bank cashier J. P. DaM and spouse. Completed high school in Latin 11 in Gothenburg, Bachelor of Arts in Lund in 1913, Master of Arts in 1915, trial year at Stockholm's public school system in 1917. Traveled to Norway in 1915 and 1935, Denmark in 1921, Germany, Austria, and Switzerland in 1922, Finland in 1927, Germany in 1931, and Britain in 1941. Was an assistant teacher in 1915, a substitute teacher in home economics in Tomelilla in 1915-16, in Mellrude in 1916, in Ronneby and Huskvarna in 1918-19, a regular home economics teacher in Karlskoga in 1919, a subject teacher at Skövde high school from 1929 and a high school teacher there from 1939.
